select clientIp, dateTime, statusCode, bytesSent, substr(referer, 0,35) as referer, substr(userAgent, 0,20) as userAgent
from accesslogs where statusCode != 200 and bytesSent > 500
order by clientIp asc, statusCode asc, dateTime asc
